Class ConformanceProvider

java.lang.Object
au.csiro.pathling.fhir.ConformanceProvider
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cacheable, IServerConformanceProvider<CapabilityStatement>
@Component @Profile("server") public class ConformanceProvider extends Object implements IServerConformanceProvider<CapabilityStatement>, Cacheable
This class provides a customised CapabilityStatement describing the functionality of the analytics server.
